
=Bio=

"Infinitely curious synthesizer and possibilist, exploring new economic models and platforms for organizational design.  Involved with SENSORICA and Metamaps in specifying the architecture of Open Value Networks, in particular the design of value equations and governance equations based on a standardized model of value dimensions and reward dimensions.  Interested in post-monetary economics.  Strong desire to understand the fundamental inputs to value creation, activities which create a higher probability of value creation, and incentive behavior linkages.  Exploring the membrane between Open Value Networks and the current societal infrastructure (legal, financial, contractual).  Looking to hack the old system to create the new.  Viral insertion into cultural operating system.  Want to expose the current assumptions, frame them as choices, then help people explore alternatives.  Oriented toward maximizing the freedom to choose one's social contract and the transparency to tell the difference."


